cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "Stratum: A QoS Substrate for ns-3 Composing DiffServ, L4S, and CAKE"
message: >-
  If you use this software in academic work, please cite both the
  software (this entry, repository-code) and the substrate paper
  (preferred-citation below) once it is published.  When reproducing
  ns-2 results specifically, also cite the 2001 thesis and the 2002
  ISCC paper (references below); the ns-2 sources are deposited as a
  separate archival Zenodo record (DOI 10.5281/zenodo.19665019).
type: software
